---
import Button from '../ui/Button.astro';
---

<section class="py-16">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <!-- Image -->
      <div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
        <img src="/images/syj-family-photo.webp" alt="The Sansford family with their RV" class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg" />
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-dark mb-4">
          Full-Time RVers &amp; Cybersecurity Professionals
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Jennifer Sansford and her family have been living full-time on the road, and like you, they quickly discovered how exposed traveling families really are. That firsthand experience is what drove them to build Shield Your Journey — protection designed by RVers, for RVers.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Our mission is simple: give mobile families the same level of protection that most people only get when they're rooted in one place. Legal access, identity monitoring, and real cybersecurity — bundled for the way you actually live.
        </p>
        <Button href="/about/" variant="secondary">
          Learn Our Story
        </Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
